{"tid":717782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"京法院判定「喬丹體育」商標有欺騙性　駁回該公司商標註冊訴求","createTime":"2018-06-26T09:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T10:00:58.000Z","uid":182758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c371dd3746fa166f32ba23597aae29e23850846c","tid":717782,"uid":182758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"NBA退役球星米高佐敦（Michael Jordan）就控告內地運動品牌「喬丹體育」涉嫌侵犯其姓名權案，於2016年底在最高人民法院上訴得直，搶回內地譯名「喬丹」的商標。<br />\n<br />\n事後，國家工商行政管理總​​局商標評審委員會駁回「喬丹體育」的商標註冊申請。喬丹體育公司不服其決定，起訴至北京知識產權法院。<br />\n<br />\n法院近日就此案作出裁決，認定「喬丹體育」的商標有欺騙性，而且該商標損害Michael Jordan的姓名權，因而駁回喬丹體育公司的訴訟請求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/174927_f4015554abfe5ee2ff4636206b0cfd76.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F174927_f4015554abfe5ee2ff4636206b0cfd76.gif&h=25154cb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eea2b01b22fca37d14c63334914b89f8e8a7dd1","tid":717782,"uid":73722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"支那仲有mike,nile,addidas,abidas,addas,bappa,kppaa,rebok,reebbok,rebook,supereme,supeeme&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b80f45466eca86c054fe9ac35785702786d39795","tid":717782,"uid":86809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"要抄都抄得醒d丫大佬<br />\n求其搵張相拍埋去都一模一樣<br />\n想幫都幫你唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c31212d0543936e1904a0f37c38e96ba7f26da","tid":717782,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80f45466eca86c054fe9ac35785702786d39795","tid":717782,"uid":86809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"要抄都抄得醒d丫大佬<br />\n求其搵張相拍埋去都一模一樣<br />\n想幫都幫你唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"原本就打算去勒索jordon，唔似點得"},{"pid":"bd4f9f332fd69449b4ac272b8e47af982af6a75e","tid":717782,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"之前唔係判Jordan 輸？"}]}